body: ### A beautiful, Open Source unofficial Mac App for [Product Hunt](https://www.producthunt.com/) ---------- ## :cloud: Download Feline ( Mac ) v0.0.1 beta ![Feline](http://i.imgur.com/pREGiX8.jpg "Mockup") ## :blush: Contribute * Feature Request, Bugs and Ideas can be added [here.](https://github.com/arjunkomath/Feline-Desktop-App/issues) ## :two_hearts: Thanks * [Product Hunt Team :)](https://www.producthunt.com/about) * [Github - Electron](http://electron.atom.io/) ## :heart_eyes: About Author * Built with <3 by [Arjun Komath](https://twitter.com/arjunz) / [arjunkomath@gmail.com](mailto:arjunkomath@gmail.com) ## :copyright: License * See the [LICENSE](https://github.com/arjunkomath/Feline-Desktop-App/blob/master/LICENSE) file for license rights and limitations (MIT).
